# Project Structure - img-tools

## Overview
This is a React application built with TypeScript that provides image manipulation tools including conversion between formats and metadata removal.

## Core Structure
- `/src` - Main source code directory
  - `App.tsx` - Main application component with routing configuration
  - `main.tsx` - Application entry point
  - `index.css` - Global styles

## Key Directories

### Components
- `/components` - Reusable UI components
  - `Header.tsx` - Application header/navigation
  - `Footer.tsx` - Page footer
  - `ImageDropZone.tsx` - Drag and drop interface for images
  - `ImagePreview.tsx` - Image preview display
  - `ImageDiffModal.tsx` - Modal for comparing images
  - `ImageMetadataModal.tsx` - Modal for viewing image metadata
  - `/ui` - Basic UI components (Shadcn/UI style)
    - UI primitives like buttons, inputs, modals, etc.

### Pages
- `/pages` - Application page components
  - `LandingPage.tsx` - Home page
  - `ImageConverter.tsx` - Image format conversion tool
  - `ImageMetadataRemover.tsx` - Tool for removing metadata from images

### Services
- `/services` - Business logic and external interactions
  - `imageService.ts` - Image processing logic (conversion, resize)
  - `metadataService.ts` - Metadata extraction and removal
  - `fileService.ts` - File handling utilities

### Utils & Constants
- `/utils` - Utility functions
  - `formatUtils.ts` - Format-related helper functions
  - `imageUtils.ts` - Image processing helpers
- `/constants` - Application constants
  - `routes.ts` - URL route definitions

### Assets
- `/assets` - Static assets like images
  - `react.svg` - React logo

## Tech Stack
- React
- React Router
- TypeScript
- TailwindCSS v4
- Shadcn: For component that does not exist in ui folder, please install it first using `npx shadcn@latest add <component_name>`

